Two findings are already partially handled in the current tree: block transaction validation no longer defaults to skipping hardfork checks, and blob admission already reads `maxBlobGasPerBlock`. I’m checking whether the remaining parts still have real narrow fixes, especially typed transaction gating and pre-Shanghai withdrawals.
